inclinations, will enjoy Surg<NOTE N="b" PLACE="foot">Heaven.</NOTE> for a
time; but the &s;ouls of tho&s;e who are holy, &s;hall be ab&s;orbed into God,
never more to reanimate fle&s;h. The wicked &s;hall be puni&s;h|ed in
