</SP> 
<SP>
<PB N="lv" REF="64">
<SPEAKER>NARUD.</SPEAKER>
<P>Thou, O father, do&s;t mention God as one; yet we are told, that
R&acirc;m, whom we are taught to call God, was born in the hou&s;e of
Je&s;&s;arit: That Ki&s;hen, whom we call God, was born in the hou&s;e of
